{"tid":939670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人以前係分唔到古巨基同方力申?","createTime":"2018-12-13T10:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T11:09:47.000Z","uid":95571,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"86a78d9dd48279403ee9c1c48eb49cefd911ffd2","tid":939670,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪得我一個係咁?<br />\n細細個真係分唔到 兩個都同期紅 樣覺得都幾似<br />\n個髮型都好似(2000年個時D台/日風）<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ent/y/2008-08-05/U1817P28T3D2127841F329DT20080805122428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fy%2F2008-08-05%2FU1817P28T3D2127841F329DT20080805122428.jpg&h=503f6a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋兩個個名都好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所以細個電視話方力申點點點時<br />\n我都諗左一陣究竟係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻眼有殺氣個個?定係個樣溫和D個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd86972579431d76f4cff48d3173bdf928be2db","tid":939670,"uid":181527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"驗眼好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97657a89edf655455366549d8819c595e5d83f3","tid":939670,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bmui0je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmui0je.jpg&h=12734420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12387d306757a950ec1e8128df49a9f12a8cda59","tid":939670,"uid":44364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"咁都分唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1976172bd8572461645cf4863e5c8777ec178e5d","tid":939670,"uid":8175,"like":4,"dislike"